<figureCitation box="[536,660,1464,1490]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="13.[151,250,1310,1335]" captionTargetBox="[176,1415,184,1284]" captionTargetId="figure@13.[170,1418,181,1284]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 4. Fauveliopsis brevipodus Hartman, 1971, n. comb., holotype (USNM 55546), A. Dorsal view. B. Anterior region, dorsal view. C. Posterior region, dorsal view. Paratypes (USNM 55547). D. Oblique dorsal view. E. Dorsal view. Scale bars: A: 260 µm, B: 100 µm, C: 90 µm, D, E: 0.4 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3335208/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Fig. 4B, C</figureCitation>
